reviewText: Don't know how to describe it. But if you have seen it and like a warp sense of humor this is it. Funnnnnny!

I bought these DVDs for my girlfriend as an Xmas present.  She loves Squidbillies, and this is everything to date, plus some extras.  We had a blast watching all of them; I found several episodes on these DVDs that I hadn't seen on Adult Swim!!!
